HEADWORD: Aposematic
<hw>Ap`o*se*mat"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>apo-</ets> + <ets>sematic</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Having or designating conspicuous or warning colors or structures
indicative of special means of defense against enemies, as in the
skunk.</def>⟦br⟧
